  "extension": {
    "lang": "EN",
    "description": "<p>The Harmonised Index of Consumer Prices (HICP)\u202fmeasures price changes\u202fof\u202fvarious consumer goods and services\u202fover time\u202f(inflation).\u202fThe annual rate of change is the percentage change in one month compared to the same month of the previous year,\u202falso called annual inflation.\u202fIt is calculated from the monthly indices and rounded to one decimal place.&nbsp;</p><p>Please note that this dataset is discontinued and replaced by dataset <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/databrowser/view/prc_hicp_minr__custom_20294338/bookmark/table?lang=en&amp;bookmarkId=02781dd9-8d8b-4586-be8d-eda8b846cf1d&amp;c=1772180209479\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36);\">prc_hicp_minr</a></p>",
